Package: PONG2
Type: Package
Title: Pulling Out NK cell Genomics (PONG2) -- KIR Genotype Imputation with Attribute Bagging
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-02-18
Description: PONG2 is a modification of HIBAG designed to impute KIR alleles from chromosome 19 SNP data.  
  It uses attribute bagging and an ensemble classifier method with haplotype inference for SNPs and KIR types.  
  Models are built from global populations in the 1000 Genomes Project.  
  Please note: For best compatibility, use R version < 4.0 or ensure Rcpp is up-to-date.
